text.data-name: Two iconic looks meet as the LEGO Group brings its instantly recognizable aesthetics to the classic Superstar. Featuring custom-made shell toe, serrated 3-Stripes and heel, carefully crafted to replicate the LEGO® brick in black and white.

text.data-name: This product is made with recycled content as part of our ambition to end plastic waste. 20% of pieces used to make the upper are made with minimum 50% recycled content.
